      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ibn Fazzal, from Yunus Bin Yaqoub, from Abu Asama, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The perfume is from the <span class=\"iTxt\">Sunnah</span> of the <span class=\"iTxt\">Mursil</span> Prophets<sup>as</sup>’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from ibn Faddal from Yunus ibn Ya’qub from abu Usamah who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Using perfume is of the discipline of the Messengers ‘Alayhim al-Salam.’” "
        ]
      }
